gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 113, Raptors 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Raptors, 113-104. Nikola Jokic led the way with 31 points, 15 rebounds, and six assists for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 20 points, six assists, and four rebounds in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 30 points, 10 rebounds, and five assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 19-10 in the regular season, while the Raptors fall to 11-16.
